WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:03.310
Hey, good morning family. I just have a

00:00:03.320 --> 00:00:05.789
video I want to do for you all today.

00:00:05.799 --> 00:00:07.150
I've been praying and asking

00:00:07.160 --> 00:00:09.750
the Lord what he's wanting me to talk

00:00:09.760 --> 00:00:12.350
to you about, and I have a

00:00:12.360 --> 00:00:14.629
direction I think I need to go. The

00:00:14.639 --> 00:00:16.430
next two things I'm going to tell you

00:00:16.440 --> 00:00:18.349
about were open-eyed visions. When I was

00:00:18.349 --> 00:00:18.359
praying—just

00:00:18.359 --> 00:00:19.910
like I

00:00:19.920 --> 00:00:21.509
am right here in this chair right

00:00:21.509 --> 00:00:21.519
now—all

00:00:21.519 --> 00:00:23.310
of a sudden the Lord opened a

00:00:23.320 --> 00:00:26.470
portal above me. I saw a massive portal

00:00:26.480 --> 00:00:28.669
open because I just asked him, 'How's

00:00:28.679 --> 00:00:30.589
your day today, Lord? What

00:00:30.589 --> 00:00:30.599
were

00:00:30.599 --> 00:00:31.870
you about? What were you

00:00:31.880 --> 00:00:34.150
doing today?'I was just

00:00:34.160 --> 00:00:35.510
curious, talking to him

00:00:35.520 --> 00:00:37.750
like I normally do, and all of a sudden

00:00:37.760 --> 00:00:39.790
he said, 'Brandon, I'll show you what I was

00:00:39.790 --> 00:00:39.800
doing,'and

00:00:39.800 --> 00:00:42.869
he opened up a portal over my

00:00:42.879 --> 00:00:46.510
living room. I saw

00:00:46.510 --> 00:00:46.520
him—and

00:00:46.520 --> 00:00:49.750
this is pretty

00:00:49.750 --> 00:00:49.760
cool—getting

00:00:49.760 --> 00:00:52.790
our table

00:00:52.800 --> 00:00:54.189
ready for our

00:00:54.199 --> 00:00:59.270
banquet: massive tables

00:00:59.280 --> 00:01:03.310
for a reception for us when we come

00:01:03.320 --> 00:01:08.590
home. Every plate was so perfect, but

00:01:08.600 --> 00:01:12.670
every plate was different. One was a

00:01:12.680 --> 00:01:16.310
flower, but my plate that was in front of

00:01:16.320 --> 00:01:18.630
me, he showed me in the spirit realm. I

00:01:18.640 --> 00:01:20.830
looked up and I could see the tables,

00:01:20.840 --> 00:01:24.350
and the plates were perfect. It was

00:01:24.360 --> 00:01:27.429
a perfect lily, but it was almost

00:01:27.439 --> 00:01:30.190
transparent. It was red

00:01:30.200 --> 00:01:33.469
and it had all the beautiful designs on

00:01:33.479 --> 00:01:36.670
this plate. On the plate was a name

00:01:36.680 --> 00:01:39.710
card, and my name was written on the

00:01:39.720 --> 00:01:42.670
plate as a

00:01:42.680 --> 00:01:46.709
reserved seat for me for this banquet

00:01:46.719 --> 00:01:49.109
that we will partake in

00:01:49.119 --> 00:01:50.630
when the Rapture of the

00:01:50.640 --> 00:01:52.350
church happens. This is one of the first

00:01:52.360 --> 00:01:55.670
things that happens: I saw a banquet, a party he

00:01:55.680 --> 00:01:58.270
has for us. It is a massive

00:01:58.280 --> 00:02:01.069
celebration of us coming home.

00:02:01.079 --> 00:02:03.429
All of the plates were perfect,

00:02:03.439 --> 00:02:04.789
like I said, and then we had these

00:02:04.799 --> 00:02:07.510
glasses, and all the glasses were

00:02:07.520 --> 00:02:10.150
this fine crystal that I've never seen

00:02:10.160 --> 00:02:12.710
on this Earth before.

00:02:12.720 --> 00:02:15.990
The glasses were beautiful, and

00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:18.750
you could see the forks, and the

00:02:18.760 --> 00:02:21.309
forks were perfect. They had all the

00:02:21.319 --> 00:02:24.030
forks lined up, and they had a

00:02:24.040 --> 00:02:26.910
napkin, the plates, and

00:02:26.920 --> 00:02:29.949
all the beautiful

00:02:29.949 --> 00:02:29.959
place

00:02:29.959 --> 00:02:32.190
setting.

00:02:34.879 --> 00:02:36.949
You could see the people that I was

00:02:36.959 --> 00:02:38.990
familiar with from this Earth—my friends, the people that

00:02:39.000 --> 00:02:40.830
I know

00:02:40.840 --> 00:02:42.830
are born again. My wife had

00:02:42.840 --> 00:02:45.630
her place next to me, and other people

00:02:45.640 --> 00:02:47.710
that I love, like family members,

00:02:47.720 --> 00:02:49.830
had their

00:02:49.840 --> 00:02:52.630
name tags in their reserved

00:02:52.630 --> 00:02:52.640
plates

00:02:52.640 --> 00:02:56.670
all around us. I

00:02:56.680 --> 00:02:58.869
could see directly around me

00:02:58.879 --> 00:03:01.110
all the beautiful things, but everybody's

00:03:01.120 --> 00:03:04.470
stuff was personalized to them. It

00:03:04.480 --> 00:03:08.270
wasn't just one type of plate

00:03:08.270 --> 00:03:08.280
or

00:03:08.280 --> 00:03:10.589
one type of glass; it was personalized

00:03:10.599 --> 00:03:12.470
to the desires of your heart, what was

00:03:12.480 --> 00:03:14.309
inside of you. It was beautiful what he

00:03:14.319 --> 00:03:17.070
had done. In the centers of the

00:03:17.080 --> 00:03:22.070
table were these flower

00:03:22.080 --> 00:03:24.070
arrangements that were the most

00:03:24.080 --> 00:03:25.949
beautiful flower

00:03:25.959 --> 00:03:28.910
arrangements:

00:03:28.910 --> 00:03:28.920
lilies,

00:03:28.920 --> 00:03:32.990
white roses, and they had

00:03:32.990 --> 00:03:33.000
this

00:03:33.000 --> 00:03:35.470
tulle.

00:03:35.480 --> 00:03:38.750
There was drapery all coming out

00:03:38.760 --> 00:03:40.949
of these trees. There were trees—and I

00:03:40.959 --> 00:03:42.390
don't know where these trees came from—like these

00:03:42.400 --> 00:03:46.070
huge, massive oak trees like you would

00:03:46.080 --> 00:03:48.229
see in Louisiana at those

00:03:48.239 --> 00:03:51.589
plantation houses. It was an outside area,

00:03:51.589 --> 00:03:51.599
not

00:03:51.599 --> 00:03:54.190
in a building or a

00:03:54.200 --> 00:03:57.470
palace.

00:03:57.480 --> 00:03:59.990
This reception is outside. There was

00:04:00.000 --> 00:04:02.030
green grass all around, and there

00:04:02.030 --> 00:04:02.040
were

00:04:02.040 --> 00:04:05.670
beautiful trees all

00:04:05.680 --> 00:04:08.949
covering the top.

00:04:08.959 --> 00:04:11.589
There was drapery all coming

00:04:11.599 --> 00:04:14.390
down from these trees all underneath

00:04:14.400 --> 00:04:16.469
where the banquet's at.

00:04:16.479 --> 00:04:18.430
There were

00:04:18.430 --> 00:04:18.440
diamond-like

00:04:18.440 --> 00:04:23.590
beads

00:04:23.600 --> 00:04:25.110
and

00:04:25.120 --> 00:04:28.270
pearls

00:04:28.280 --> 00:04:30.270
hanging out of the trees,

00:04:30.280 --> 00:04:34.510
all fastened with the

00:04:34.510 --> 00:04:34.520
tulle,

00:04:34.520 --> 00:04:38.510
all this beautiful white silk

00:04:38.510 --> 00:04:38.520
and

00:04:38.520 --> 00:04:41.510
mesh; the pearls were wrapped in

00:04:41.510 --> 00:04:41.520
it.

00:04:41.520 --> 00:04:43.510
It was gold, and

00:04:43.520 --> 00:04:45.110
you could see all the colors. It was

00:04:45.120 --> 00:04:48.070
draped and it was so decorated—so

00:04:48.070 --> 00:04:48.080
perfect—it

00:04:48.080 --> 00:04:50.830
was like a wedding reception.

00:04:50.840 --> 00:04:53.430
Everything was just

00:04:53.440 --> 00:04:57.150
immaculate and gorgeous. I try to

00:04:57.160 --> 00:04:59.469
capture and tell you everything

00:04:59.479 --> 00:05:01.390
the Lord showed me.

00:05:01.400 --> 00:05:04.070
There were some kind of

00:05:04.080 --> 00:05:06.590
little lights—and

00:05:06.590 --> 00:05:06.600
this

00:05:06.600 --> 00:05:08.510
sounds really

00:05:08.510 --> 00:05:08.520
weird—like

00:05:08.520 --> 00:05:12.189
twinkle lights inside of the

00:05:12.189 --> 00:05:12.199
tulle

00:05:12.199 --> 00:05:15.830
and the pearls.

00:05:15.840 --> 00:05:20.350
It was absolutely gorgeous. Everything—the

00:05:20.350 --> 00:05:20.360
place

00:05:20.360 --> 00:05:23.390
settings,

00:05:23.400 --> 00:05:26.150
the vases with flowers, and everything—it

00:05:26.150 --> 00:05:26.160
was

00:05:26.160 --> 00:05:30.870
so precious,

00:05:30.880 --> 00:05:34.150
his celebration for us when we come home.

00:05:34.160 --> 00:05:36.790
This is another time I was praying; these

00:05:36.790 --> 00:05:36.800
were

00:05:36.800 --> 00:05:39.070
two different times.

00:05:39.080 --> 00:05:41.629
Again, I

00:05:41.639 --> 00:05:43.670
always ask the Lord, 'How's your day today?

00:05:43.680 --> 00:05:45.909
How

00:05:45.909 --> 00:05:45.919
are

00:05:45.919 --> 00:05:47.710
things

00:05:47.710 --> 00:05:47.720
going?'just

00:05:47.720 --> 00:05:49.390
like I'm talking to a

00:05:49.400 --> 00:05:51.430
friend. He's my best friend, so

00:05:51.440 --> 00:05:52.629
it's like talking to your friend

00:05:52.639 --> 00:05:54.029
on the telephone. I always

00:05:54.039 --> 00:05:56.270
ask, 'How's your day today?

00:05:56.280 --> 00:05:58.189
What did you do today?'or

00:05:58.189 --> 00:05:58.199
like

00:05:58.199 --> 00:05:59.990
you talk to your

00:05:59.990 --> 00:06:00.000
spouse.

00:06:00.000 --> 00:06:03.510
I

00:06:03.510 --> 00:06:03.520
asked

00:06:03.520 --> 00:06:05.350
how his day

00:06:05.360 --> 00:06:07.870
was—'How

00:06:07.880 --> 00:06:10.230
was your day today? What

00:06:10.240 --> 00:06:12.589
all went on?'—and all of a sudden

00:06:12.599 --> 00:06:14.270
he said, 'Hi, Brandon,'and he started

00:06:14.280 --> 00:06:16.350
talking to me again. He said, 'I

00:06:16.360 --> 00:06:19.029
want to show you what we're doing

00:06:19.039 --> 00:06:21.830
today.'He

00:06:21.840 --> 00:06:25.029
said they're having a

00:06:25.039 --> 00:06:27.950
reception practice, a parade practice. He

00:06:27.960 --> 00:06:30.830
said, 'When you come home

00:06:30.840 --> 00:06:33.070
in the Rapture, son, we are going

00:06:33.080 --> 00:06:36.950
to have a massive

00:06:36.950 --> 00:06:36.960
home-welcoming

00:06:36.960 --> 00:06:40.309
party for

00:06:40.309 --> 00:06:40.319
you.'Everybody

00:06:40.319 --> 00:06:43.350
that has died before you,

00:06:43.360 --> 00:06:45.230
they're waiting for you, and we are going

00:06:45.240 --> 00:06:48.270
to celebrate all the people—this massive

00:06:48.280 --> 00:06:50.749
amount of the church that is coming

00:06:50.759 --> 00:06:53.070
home in the Rapture. He said we're

00:06:53.080 --> 00:06:55.909
going to have a massive parade.

00:06:55.919 --> 00:06:59.629
It's a

00:06:59.639 --> 00:07:02.189
reception, but I could see the

00:07:02.199 --> 00:07:05.350
people and they had banners. He showed me

00:07:05.360 --> 00:07:07.270
what they were doing: Jesus was riding a

00:07:07.280 --> 00:07:10.189
white horse,

00:07:10.199 --> 00:07:12.430
and he was the head of the

00:07:12.440 --> 00:07:14.909
reception of what they were

00:07:14.919 --> 00:07:17.230
practicing, and all the people kept

00:07:17.240 --> 00:07:20.790
saying, 'For the Lord is good, and his

00:07:20.800 --> 00:07:23.990
mercy endureth forever,'as he was riding

00:07:24.000 --> 00:07:26.390
on this horse in heaven. I

00:07:26.400 --> 00:07:28.309
could see the streets of gold. I could

00:07:28.319 --> 00:07:31.790
see the people on both sides

00:07:31.800 --> 00:07:33.510
of the streets, just like

00:07:33.510 --> 00:07:33.520
the

00:07:33.520 --> 00:07:36.749
Macy's Thanksgiving Day Parade.

00:07:36.759 --> 00:07:38.950
Both sides of the street

00:07:38.960 --> 00:07:41.869
had people all lining the

00:07:41.869 --> 00:07:41.879
way; it looked

00:07:41.879 --> 00:07:44.469
like a massive town, like a

00:07:44.479 --> 00:07:47.790
city. I could see buildings on both

00:07:47.790 --> 00:07:47.800
sides—massive

00:07:47.800 --> 00:07:50.230
buildings all

00:07:50.240 --> 00:07:52.629
beautifully designed, kind of like you

00:07:52.639 --> 00:07:57.149
would see in Europe, with old English-style tile roofs.

00:07:57.149 --> 00:07:57.159
It was beautiful,

00:07:57.159 --> 00:08:00.950
like

00:08:05.720 --> 00:08:08.749
a downtown area

00:08:08.759 --> 00:08:12.390
in heaven. I could see the

00:08:12.390 --> 00:08:12.400
people,

00:08:12.400 --> 00:08:14.070
and Jesus was

00:08:14.080 --> 00:08:16.510
riding on the gold street on his horse,

00:08:16.520 --> 00:08:18.550
and people

00:08:18.550 --> 00:08:18.560
had

00:08:18.560 --> 00:08:21.629
those kingly banners that

00:08:21.629 --> 00:08:21.639
said

00:08:21.639 --> 00:08:24.589
'King of Kings'and 'Lord of

00:08:24.589 --> 00:08:24.599
Lords.'All

00:08:24.599 --> 00:08:27.070
the banners were

00:08:27.080 --> 00:08:29.749
going down the street, and people

00:08:29.759 --> 00:08:32.230
were celebrating

00:08:32.230 --> 00:08:32.240
and

00:08:32.240 --> 00:08:34.430
rejoicing.

00:08:34.440 --> 00:08:36.149
This is going to sound really crazy,

00:08:36.159 --> 00:08:38.709
but there was

00:08:38.719 --> 00:08:40.550
gold

00:08:40.560 --> 00:08:43.469
confetti in the air, and people were celebrating.

00:08:43.479 --> 00:08:44.710
They were practicing,

00:08:44.720 --> 00:08:47.470
getting ready for the coming of

00:08:47.480 --> 00:08:49.389
the church.

00:08:54.040 --> 00:08:55.910
He said, 'We're

00:08:55.920 --> 00:08:58.069
getting ready for you, son. We're getting

00:08:58.079 --> 00:09:01.430
ready for the church!'I got so

00:09:01.440 --> 00:09:04.110
excited because I could see all the

00:09:04.120 --> 00:09:06.990
people rejoicing, and they

00:09:07.000 --> 00:09:09.509
kept saying, 'For he is good,

00:09:09.519 --> 00:09:12.750
and his mercy endures forever.'I

00:09:12.750 --> 00:09:12.760
could

00:09:12.760 --> 00:09:15.269
hear all the people, and

00:09:15.279 --> 00:09:16.949
he was riding

00:09:20.959 --> 00:09:24.310
his horse.

00:09:24.320 --> 00:09:27.910
His horse had a bridle that was covered in jewels. His horse was

00:09:27.910 --> 00:09:27.920
beautiful

00:09:27.920 --> 00:09:30.990
and had

00:09:30.990 --> 00:09:31.000
a

00:09:31.000 --> 00:09:32.710
chest piece

00:09:32.710 --> 00:09:32.720
with

00:09:32.720 --> 00:09:34.430
beautiful diamonds,

00:09:34.440 --> 00:09:36.870
emeralds,

00:09:36.880 --> 00:09:40.389
sapphires, and rubies.

00:09:42.519 --> 00:09:45.389
He

00:09:45.399 --> 00:09:47.750
was riding his horse

00:09:47.760 --> 00:09:50.190
through the

00:09:50.200 --> 00:09:52.310
town,

00:09:52.320 --> 00:09:54.710
being worshipped in

00:09:54.720 --> 00:09:56.750
heaven. I

00:09:56.750 --> 00:09:56.760
was

00:09:56.760 --> 00:09:58.389
just

00:10:01.000 --> 00:10:10.990
in awe

00:10:10.990 --> 00:10:11.000
of

00:10:11.000 --> 00:10:17.509
how much he loves

00:10:17.519 --> 00:10:20.389
us, how much he

00:10:20.399 --> 00:10:24.630
cares, and all the personal

00:10:24.640 --> 00:10:27.910
detail he takes the

00:10:27.920 --> 00:10:31.710
time just to love on his

00:10:31.720 --> 00:10:34.470
people. People have no idea how much

00:10:34.480 --> 00:10:36.550
Jesus loves

00:10:36.560 --> 00:10:40.389
you and how much he takes

00:10:40.399 --> 00:10:44.269
thought for every

00:10:46.560 --> 00:10:51.110
detail, from the plates

00:10:51.120 --> 00:10:54.350
to the forks to the

00:10:54.360 --> 00:10:57.230
parade. He's so excited for his children

00:10:57.240 --> 00:10:59.509
to come home.

00:10:59.519 --> 00:11:05.509
He's waiting on us, and when God says

00:11:05.509 --> 00:11:05.519
'Go,'he's

00:11:05.519 --> 00:11:07.430
coming back for

00:11:07.440 --> 00:11:09.990
us, and we're going to rule and reign

00:11:10.000 --> 00:11:11.829
with him

00:11:11.839 --> 00:11:16.949
forever and ever. For the King, he is good.

00:11:16.959 --> 00:11:25.870
Jesus is good, and his mercy endures

00:11:25.880 --> 00:11:31.590
forever. There was a bridge

00:11:31.600 --> 00:11:34.230
with a huge river going through

00:11:34.240 --> 00:11:38.190
it. The town was right here

00:11:38.200 --> 00:11:40.030
on this side,

00:11:40.040 --> 00:11:43.629
and the gold

00:11:43.639 --> 00:11:46.670
street went over

00:11:46.680 --> 00:11:49.790
this bridge. There was a river

00:11:54.399 --> 00:11:57.470
flowing out of the

00:11:57.470 --> 00:11:57.480
throne—Living

00:11:57.480 --> 00:11:59.990
Water.

00:12:00.000 --> 00:12:02.550
There

00:12:02.550 --> 00:12:02.560
were

00:12:02.560 --> 00:12:04.509
steps that went

00:12:04.519 --> 00:12:08.470
up after this huge bridge over the

00:12:08.480 --> 00:12:10.790
river, there was green on both sides, and

00:12:10.800 --> 00:12:12.710
there was this

00:12:14.639 --> 00:12:17.829
beautiful

00:12:20.550 --> 00:12:20.560
castle-looking

00:12:23.240 --> 00:12:27.310
building

00:12:27.320 --> 00:12:29.710
where he was riding his horse.

00:12:29.720 --> 00:12:31.550
All the people were there

00:12:31.550 --> 00:12:31.560
in

00:12:31.560 --> 00:12:33.949
their gowns. This is what's really

00:12:33.959 --> 00:12:37.389
amazing too: everyone

00:12:37.389 --> 00:12:37.399
worshipping

00:12:37.399 --> 00:12:39.350
him on those horses had

00:12:39.360 --> 00:12:42.230
different gowns; not one gown or robe was the

00:12:42.240 --> 00:12:45.509
same.

00:12:45.519 --> 00:12:47.230
There

00:12:47.230 --> 00:12:47.240
were

00:12:47.240 --> 00:12:49.629
different colors—everyone thinks

00:12:49.639 --> 00:12:51.990
it's just white gowns, but there were robes

00:12:52.000 --> 00:12:55.030
with colors.

00:12:57.399 --> 00:13:00.230
Some people had

00:13:00.240 --> 00:13:02.949
robes and some had gowns, but there

00:13:02.949 --> 00:13:02.959
were

00:13:02.959 --> 00:13:06.470
more gowns than

00:13:06.480 --> 00:13:09.269
robes. It looked like a lot of

00:13:09.279 --> 00:13:11.030
people just had a gown of

00:13:11.040 --> 00:13:13.230
salvation; they were just

00:13:13.240 --> 00:13:14.750
born again and had a revelation

00:13:14.750 --> 00:13:14.760
of

00:13:14.760 --> 00:13:18.069
getting saved. The

00:13:18.079 --> 00:13:20.189
people who had robes had beautiful

00:13:20.199 --> 00:13:23.750
colors

00:13:23.750 --> 00:13:23.760
with

00:13:23.760 --> 00:13:26.550
emblems and things of honor for what

00:13:26.560 --> 00:13:29.990
you did on the earth

00:13:30.000 --> 00:13:32.790
for him.

00:13:35.440 --> 00:13:36.870
There

00:13:36.880 --> 00:13:40.189
were thick, beautiful robes.

00:13:40.199 --> 00:13:43.310
I couldn't see the people's faces

00:13:43.310 --> 00:13:43.320
because

00:13:43.320 --> 00:13:45.069
they

00:13:45.079 --> 00:13:47.430
were facing

00:13:47.430 --> 00:13:47.440
away,

00:13:47.440 --> 00:13:49.790
their backs toward

00:13:49.800 --> 00:13:51.949
me.

00:13:51.959 --> 00:13:53.430
On the other side of the street, I

00:13:53.440 --> 00:13:55.790
could see the people a little

00:13:55.800 --> 00:13:59.470
bit, and they were all lining the

00:13:59.480 --> 00:14:03.269
streets.

00:14:11.199 --> 00:14:14.949
I look forward to

00:14:14.959 --> 00:14:17.110
it: the

00:14:17.120 --> 00:14:19.870
peace, the

00:14:19.880 --> 00:14:27.590
presence. Oh,

00:14:27.600 --> 00:14:32.030
Jesus. I take myself back when I talk

00:14:32.040 --> 00:14:33.629
about

00:14:33.639 --> 00:14:38.150
it; I can feel

00:14:38.160 --> 00:14:41.670
the feeling I had

00:14:41.670 --> 00:14:41.680
when I saw

00:14:41.680 --> 00:14:44.230
him on his

00:14:44.240 --> 00:14:47.509
horse. He had a

00:14:49.800 --> 00:14:51.350
crown

00:14:51.360 --> 00:14:54.470
on that was beautiful and

00:14:54.480 --> 00:14:56.990
towered above his head, covered

00:14:56.990 --> 00:14:57.000
in

00:14:57.000 --> 00:15:00.150
really cool

00:15:00.150 --> 00:15:00.160
jewels.

00:15:00.160 --> 00:15:03.189
It was gorgeous. This crown

00:15:03.189 --> 00:15:03.199
had

00:15:05.870 --> 00:15:05.880
a

00:15:05.880 --> 00:15:08.509
purple

00:15:08.519 --> 00:15:12.069
banner around the bottom of it

00:15:12.079 --> 00:15:14.829
with

00:15:14.839 --> 00:15:18.310
stuff

00:15:18.320 --> 00:15:20.629
like fur.

00:15:20.639 --> 00:15:24.310
He

00:15:24.320 --> 00:15:28.189
had a cape on with

00:15:28.189 --> 00:15:28.199
a

00:15:28.199 --> 00:15:30.269
gold

00:15:30.279 --> 00:15:32.389
medallion in

00:15:32.399 --> 00:15:35.470
the middle, and his cape

00:15:35.480 --> 00:15:38.710
draped down by his legs while he was on his

00:15:42.800 --> 00:15:46.470
horse. Everything was just so perfect.

00:15:46.480 --> 00:15:48.470
So, Father, I thank you right now in the

00:15:48.480 --> 00:15:50.790
name of Jesus. I'm going to do a blanket

00:15:50.800 --> 00:15:53.749
prayer for all the people that have asked for

00:15:53.759 --> 00:15:57.790
help, all the prayer needs, the

00:15:57.800 --> 00:16:01.069
healings, and the

00:16:01.069 --> 00:16:01.079
people

00:16:01.079 --> 00:16:03.829
whose

00:16:03.839 --> 00:16:06.389
loved ones are far

00:16:06.399 --> 00:16:08.910
away from the Lord. Father, we thank you.

00:16:08.920 --> 00:16:11.670
Lord, you showed me in a vision today

00:16:14.480 --> 00:16:16.470
little birds chirping in a

00:16:16.480 --> 00:16:18.710
mama's nest, and they

00:16:18.710 --> 00:16:18.720
are

00:16:18.720 --> 00:16:21.110
asking, 'Help, help, help! Cheep,

00:16:21.110 --> 00:16:21.120
cheep, cheep!'I

00:16:21.120 --> 00:16:22.829
saw them in the spirit, Lord, and I

00:16:22.839 --> 00:16:26.030
said, 'God, there are so many mouths to feed;

00:16:26.040 --> 00:16:28.309
I can't do it

00:16:28.309 --> 00:16:28.319
all.'You

00:16:28.319 --> 00:16:31.309
said to me, 'It's my

00:16:31.319 --> 00:16:33.670
job, Brandon. The Holy Spirit will take

00:16:33.680 --> 00:16:37.069
care of this,'and I saw that big bird

00:16:37.079 --> 00:16:39.110
dump a whole bunch of worms on

00:16:39.110 --> 00:16:39.120
those

00:16:39.120 --> 00:16:42.790
little babies. Today, I pray that for

00:16:42.800 --> 00:16:45.069
you: the Holy Spirit is going to meet

00:16:45.069 --> 00:16:45.079
your

00:16:45.079 --> 00:16:47.030
every need right where you're

00:16:47.040 --> 00:16:50.150
at. Jesus has got this for you. I call

00:16:50.160 --> 00:16:52.230
healing over your bodies

00:16:52.230 --> 00:16:52.240
and

00:16:52.240 --> 00:16:54.829
deliverance over you in Jesus'name. I

00:16:54.839 --> 00:16:57.430
call restoration over your marriages.

00:17:01.519 --> 00:17:04.029
I call blessing over your

00:17:04.039 --> 00:17:06.870
home financially.

00:17:06.880 --> 00:17:08.590
Father, I pray the Lord would

00:17:08.600 --> 00:17:10.270
bless them and keep them; may his face

00:17:10.280 --> 00:17:12.630
shine upon you and be gracious to you

00:17:12.640 --> 00:17:14.669
and give you peace. I call those

00:17:14.679 --> 00:17:17.590
blessings over their home in

00:17:17.590 --> 00:17:17.600
Jesus'name,

00:17:17.600 --> 00:17:19.909
and we praise the Lord for everything

00:17:19.919 --> 00:17:22.309
he's already done and what he continues

00:17:22.319 --> 00:17:25.990
to do in your life. In the name of Jesus,

00:17:26.000 --> 00:17:28.029
put a smile on your face and a song in

00:17:28.039 --> 00:17:30.710
your heart. Jesus loves you, and I love

00:17:30.720 --> 00:17:32.430
you. I'm so thankful that you're a

00:17:32.440 --> 00:17:35.190
part of my family here. God bless you all.

00:17:35.200 --> 00:17:37.880
Bye-bye.

